<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Elisabeth von Bayern, Burggräfin von Nürnberg</head><p>Der Rat teilt mit, dass bei dem Teiding zwischen N. Zollner zu Vach und Kunz Kalb, Bürger zu Nürnberg, dessen Arztlohn wegen Verwundung nicht berücksichtigt wurde.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_78" id="38v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_78_r1l1">Eliʒabet <expan>B<ex>ur</ex>ggrefin</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_78_r1l2">Gnedıge fraw / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt / von des <expan>Cʒolln<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> cʒü </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_78_r1l3">vache / vnd des <expan>Chüncʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> kalben <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> / <expan>Laſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnade <expan>wıſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_78_r1l4">daʒ vns die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vormals vns auch yecʒunden geſagt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / daʒ in den </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_78_r1l5">teÿdingen <expan>nemlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hindan geſacʒt ſeÿ / . daʒ der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> vnſer <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> . vmb 
<del rend="strikethrough"> die </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_78_r1l6">wunden vnd arcʒtlon / wol <expan>frewntl<ex>ich</ex></expan> recht <expan>vord<ex>er</ex>n</expan> müge / . vnd wir <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_78_r1l7">auch das vormals beſtellet / daʒ er <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Cʒolln<ex>er</ex></expan> v̈ber daſſelb / als es <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_78_r1l8">in den <expan>teydinge<ex>n</ex></expan> hindan geſacʒt ıſt / nicht cʒü <expan>ſprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſülle / vnd ob <expan>yema<ex>n</ex>t</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_78_r1l9"><expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von vns <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> für geb / <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvol / daʒ Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_78_r1l10">des nicht <expan>gelawb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet / vnd wo wir etc . <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>vts<ex>upra</ex></expan> . </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_78" id="38v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Elizabet, <expan>b<ex>ur</ex>ggrefin</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnedige fraw, als ir uns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt
                        von des <expan>Czolln<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> czü Vache und des
                            <expan>Chüncze<ex>n</ex></expan> Kalben, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, <expan>lasse<ex>n</ex></expan> wir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnade <expan>wisse<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                        daz uns die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vormals und auch yeczunden gesagt
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz in den teydingen
                                <expan>nemlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hindan gesaczt sey, daz der
                                <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> unser
                            <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> umb wunden und arcztlon wol
                                <expan>frewntl<ex>ich</ex></expan> recht
                            <expan>vord<ex>er</ex>n</expan> müge. Und wir
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> auch das vormals bestellet, daz er
                                <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Czolln<ex>er</ex></expan> über dasselb, als es
                            <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> in den <expan>teydinge<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        hindan gesaczt ist, nicht czü <expan>sprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sülle; und ob
                                <expan>yema<ex>n</ex>t</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von uns <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
                        fürgeb, <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wol, daz ir des nicht
                            <expan>gelawb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet; und wo wir etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>ut s<ex>upra</ex></expan>. </ab>
</div>
